Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned' for cases involving 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and activity Completed + Resolved for cases where activity Completed + Resolved occurs

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' to transition to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum time for 'Accepted + Assigned' before transitioning to any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' grouped by 'country'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and activity Completed + Closed for cases where activity Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Average time it takes 'Accepted + Assigned' to be followed by 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total time it takes for 'Accepted + Assigned' to transition to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Resolved' in high-frequency variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in the context of resolving incidents
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' until 'Completed + In Call' is performed in the most common process variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' before reaching 'Completed + Cancelled' status
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases with 'Completed + In Call' to understand its impact on the process flow
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and activity Completed + In Call for cases where activity Completed + In Call occurs
